    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document defines a hierarchical method of encoding Join/Prune attributes that provides a more efficient encoding when the same attribute values need to be specified for multiple sources in a PIM Join/Prune message.  This document updates RFC 5384 by renaming the encoding type registry specified there.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
